      "title": "TVS - Additional Charges Ultrasound Scan at Cadabams Diagnostics – Price, Purpose & Process",
      "description": "Understand why a TVS ultrasound may carry an extra fee, what it diagnoses, how to prepare, and results timeline at Cadabams Diagnostics.",
